      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>One thing about Monique Weight Loss that is pretty incredible is how far-reaching it has proven itself to be among the populace. Indeed, it is not all that hard to see it at work in your daily life or the lives of people you know, maybe. What is curious about this is the amount of information that is generally unfamiliar to people.&nbsp;</p>
